item.description:
Karaoke!!

Let's sing Saturday night at Muldowney's Pub in downtown Providence. I have not been here yet, but I'm excited to try some new places.

Come down and sing, drink, dance, chat, meet new friends, see old friends and have a great time.

I'm told this place is CASH ONLY, so bring some paper money.

Hope to see you there!!
item.how_to_find_us: Take a gander at everyone's pictures and try to identify us. I will post something closer to the event (maybe during) about what I'm wearing and where we may be standing.
item.name: Karaoke!!! at Muldowney's Pub
